'''''Droids'' 2''' is the second issue of the [[Star Wars: Droids (1986)|''Star Wars Droids'']] series of comics. The story is split into three chapters, "The Ultimate Weapon Part 1," "The Ultimate Weapon Part 2: In the Company of Evil," and "The Ultimate Weapon Part 3: Shock Treatment." It was published on [[March 18]], [[1986]]<ref name="Marvel Age" /> with a cover date of [[June]] 1986.

==Plot summary==
[[Tig Fromm]] and [[Vlix Oncard]] kidnap the Idd family to get their hands on a high-powered laser.

